## Remarks 

<span data-ttu-id="3717f-102">可以通过实现来创建自定义请求验证类型<xref:System.Web.Util.RequestValidator>类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3717f-102">You can create a custom request validation type by implementing the <xref:System.Web.Util.RequestValidator> type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3717f-103">当 ASP.NET 调用<xref:System.Web.Util.RequestValidator.IsValidRequestString%2A>方法来验证请求，ASP.NET 将传递`requestValidationSource`参数来指定要验证的数据源。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3717f-103">When ASP.NET calls the <xref:System.Web.Util.RequestValidator.IsValidRequestString%2A> method to validate a request, ASP.NET passes a `requestValidationSource` parameter to specify the source of the data being validated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3717f-104"><xref:System.Web.Util.RequestValidationSource>枚举用于指定源或类型的正在进行验证的请求数据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3717f-104">The <xref:System.Web.Util.RequestValidationSource> enumeration is used to specify the source or kind of request data that is being validated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3717f-105">该枚举指示传入的 HTTP 输入类型`value`参数的<xref:System.Web.Util.RequestValidator.IsValidRequestString%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3717f-105">The enumeration indicates the type of HTTP input that is passed in the `value` parameter of the <xref:System.Web.Util.RequestValidator.IsValidRequestString%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3717f-106">作为一种方式回退到 HTTP 输入的基本请求验证实现，如果不希望使用自定义逻辑进行验证，可以使用枚举。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3717f-106">You can use the enumeration as a way to fall back to the base request validation implementation for HTTP inputs if you do not want to validate using custom logic.</span></span>  

